E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('117','1','eake','微博','2','马云说过，你为什么难成功，因为你睡了不该睡的人 ！ \r\n成功的因素有很多，但排名第一的成功关键是什么？你可能猜不出来。答案是：配偶，你经常睡的人。\r\n每两个顶尖成功的人中，就会有一个因为找对床伴而成功，这个因素占成功的50%，甚至是更高。','15','微信营销','http://wx.eake.cn/tpl/Static/kindeditors/attached/99630ff411650cfa/image/20141019/99630ff411650cfa2014101922260596020.jpg','1','&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;马云说过，你为什么难成功，因为你睡了不该睡的人 ！ &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n成功的因素有很多，但排名第一的成功关键是什么？你可能猜不出来。答案是：配偶，你经常睡的人。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n每两个顶尖成功的人中，就会有一个因为找对床伴而成功，这个因素占成功的50%，甚至是更高。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#7F7F7F;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n大部分人没有成功，就是因为找了一个能摧毁他的人。武大郎没能把烧饼店开到全大宋连锁，一个很重要的原因是潘金莲给他带来了毁灭。同样，那些成功的人，也有一半是因为找到了一个会激励他的枕边人。有人说，到底是克林顿娶了希拉里，才变成美国总统？还是希拉里有眼光，嫁给一个以后就会当总统的克林顿？其实，他们是在互相影响下，才成为美国历史上最般配的夫妻档的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#7F7F7F;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#7F7F7F;&quot;&gt;你的枕边人，对你成功的影响太关键了，因为你50%以上的成功掌握在睡在你身边人的手里，即使他（她）什么事都不做，他（她）却可以“催眠”你。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n睡在你身边的人，要么是来摧毁你的，要么是你的激励师。从白天到夜晚，从夜晚到白天，日复一日，年复一年，他（她）对你的期望，跟你说的话，通过θ波和α波传到你的大脑中，深深地印在你的潜意识中，最后决定了你人生的成败！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#7F7F7F;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n根据心理学家研究，别人的看法会影响我们对自己的认知。对我们影响力最大的人，前半辈子是父母，后半辈子就是枕边人。枕边人会决定我们的命运，但是枕边人是我们自己选的。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n你的成功要靠睡在你身边的人，对方要么帮你建立更好的人际关系，要么摧毁你的人际关系；不是告诉你：“你是最棒的，你一定能完成梦想。”就是告诉你：“你根本不配拥有这样的梦想。”“我已经结婚生子了，可是我的另一半还是毁人孜孜不倦，我该怎么办？难不成，离了再找一个，重新睡？”请明白，当初你的配偶选择与你结婚，偕老此生，一定是因为在对方的心目中你是优秀的。不然，如果对方明知道你不好，怎么会决定跟你过一辈子？&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n同样，在你决定跟对方结婚的时候，也一定是觉得对方是很优秀的，是可以让你发挥自己的能力，是可以助你成功的，不然，你怎么会决定与对方过一辈子？这么看来，当初，你们能相互激励，现在为什么变了呢？首先是因为你变了，所以对方也变了！&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n怎么办？先改变自己，让自己成为一个积极的懂得欣赏和激励配偶的人，根据吸引力原则，渐渐地你的配偶也会变成跟你一样的人。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n总之，睡在你身边的人，是决定你成功的第一大关健所在。你必须让他（她）变成你的助力而不是阻力。请记住：她（他）不是帮助你一飞冲天，就是把你打落地下。而决定你配偶如何做的人，是你 .......&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;我们一生会遇到三个能够改变命运的人：第1人是老师。一个人多优秀，他的导师很重要；第2人是同伴。一个人走什么样的路，能走多远，与谁同行很重要；第3人是敌人。一个人能多成功，有一个强大的对手很重要。这个对手可能是一个人，也可能是一个逆境,甚至是我们人性深处的另一个自己。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#7F7F7F;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#64451D;&quot;&gt;如果您喜欢我们的内容请动动小手指转发到您的朋友圈&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span&gt;&lt;b&gt;您还可以点击：&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MTE4OTgyNg==&amp;mid=201017818&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d4fcf7d2a518d4b3fc1d4c4f971ffc21#rd&quot;&gt;亚篮网公众服务&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;关注我们&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','1413728770','1414742685','83','99630ff411650cfa','你为什么难成功，因为你睡了不该睡的人','','117','0','0','0',NULL,'1','1','0','1','','');");
E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('121','6','1457963911','知识','1','*杰诚生活*   女人卸妆算什么！你见过旅游胜地的「卸妆照」么？太恐怖啦！','11','生活小常识','http://wx.eake.cn/uploads/2/257e21c8a9e1be8c/5/5/2/7/thumb_5445f78530312.jpg','1','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;在很久很久以&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;前有一群人关注&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;了我，然后TA们过上了幸福快乐的生活！&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;amp;mid=201415213&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚家政&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;默剧，谈嘻哈生活，说不能说的秘密，发别人不敢发的内容，我们无法自控，还有不敢说的么？每日新鲜、时尚、搞笑、情趣信息，猛点关注，快乐随行，我们做最出色的自传媒。&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【更多你喜欢的】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;点击标题上面蓝色字“&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;amp;mid=201415213&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚家政&lt;/a&gt;”关注&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	安宁杰诚家政服务有限公司\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	联系电话：0871-68681294\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size:20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	女人卸妆算什么！你见过旅游胜地的「卸妆照」么？\r\n&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【爱琴海·希腊圣托里尼】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	不知道你有没有过这样的经历，某天在杂志上看到一幅希腊圣托里尼的风景照片，这真是个把全世界蓝色都用尽的地方！林立着白色的建筑群，你仿佛感受到了来自爱琴海浓浓的海风……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWA9zyptNzic3sOPdPesEVrMduGhxZaUQSxpHib9W6u3x49xWmpAnO9C5A/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWu0ibBfKOgtbYqvkD15EKCvhPsiaJacZ8lWSt5vMZhMFmibqjFxYQp6KjQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	然而事实的真相却是……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoW80RcjIaFdUlTLEh46Bwe6dOEsdhWiayKaClCc88qULfbkmmw3Z9Yolg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	大片的赤褐色裸岩，植被稀疏，小城仅仅只是其中一块较为平坦山坡而已……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【埃及金字塔】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	漫漫黄沙覆盖着五千年古老的埃及帝国，远处矗立金字塔仿佛在述说一段尘封已久的故事……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWuiciaMr8FSuEEodzYHpDZ9ACB3w3iaAcHJqicBHy6KHUPqByaKqP7Zqibyg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	但是真相却是……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWGQv3974aP9FpNdjoKxvic4H9BhVAHwJU1U3gMRRicBnze8sBERqrkL3w/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	说好的沙漠呢？金字塔旁边就是城市⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【英国巨石阵】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	巨石呈环形屹立在绿色的旷野间，这就是英伦三岛最著名、最神秘的史前遗迹——巨石阵。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWesVRNEaGbpzkCscKaia7dPHD34NAGJDicnK2YpKofQIKDiaXT0y0pyia6Q/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	对了，需要说明的是：这次百度真的没有骗你，因为这里的确……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWjzVU7e95ib5ptIaPZBaib2GUoFcg1ib07iccffIehKAOrnfG9j6aTIm6pQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	真的只有石头………………\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【泰姬陵】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	印度知名度最高的古迹之一，会在早中晚所呈现出的面貌各不相同，早上是灿烂的金色，白天的阳光下是耀眼的白色，斜阳夕照下，白色的泰姬陵从灰黄、金黄，逐渐变成粉红、暗红、淡青色，而在月光下又成了银白色，白色大理石映着淡淡的蓝色萤光，更给人一种恍若仙境的感觉。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWsds1CcskC9Bx6UzicbfUK6X4kZjbbzE5NfBCzb7JDG64MLTa26ZqoIA/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	可惜“印度阿三”们显然没有认真的对待这样难得的古迹……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWQnG1h3V3LQ8ALEFwZABq9SMvNnZ3Xpibsuerta0cdG7Ie4JQszo0O7g/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	周围全部都是垃圾⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【勃兰登堡门】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	勃兰登堡门位于德国首都柏林的市中心，最初是柏林城墙的一道城门，因通往勃兰登堡而得名。现在保存的勃兰登堡门是一座新古典主义风格的建筑。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWXWxqQQM9PRpzWAzP5veGmdpxASTRxJEOxjjkw5mPhcwQwm0mWzicvSg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	事实上……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWz0QQDUXVFYygs8ewU9CwF9uDoEbXuSibP3iatCPDWVQOaQia9e3rzFib0A/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	没错，它真的仅仅只是一个门⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【圣家族大教堂】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	圣家族大教堂是西班牙建筑大师安东尼奥·高迪的毕生代表作。它位于西班牙加泰罗尼亚地区的巴塞罗那市区中心，始建于1882年，目前仍在在修建中。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWCdH9Fpliar9duZbUSDvG1oDbXnfcEBmia1D0l0zaKClWEsHwonX56nLw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	芒果台的《花儿与少年》节目组也曾经到过这个地方哦，当然，实际上它……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWBusianbVO5Q59FBdORPz852rIGsZqrTx8Ec7GwrGWvOW6D0jkCQBfIw/0&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	好的，实际上它周围都是楼，密密麻麻的⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【尼加拉大瀑布】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	尼加拉瀑布被认为是世上最壮观的景致之一，亦特别受到度蜜月者的欢迎。它位于加拿大和美国交界的尼亚加拉河上。号称世界7大奇景之一，丰沛而浩瀚的水汽，震撼了所有前来观赏的游人。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoW6VJFvGQGTxBG0j8znfJmDefQR65HYAibsBC4NrIE0KYloL1Oy44T2SQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	一般来说，这么壮观的自然景观应该是在远离城市的风景区是吧，但是……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWqcnFI20v3zpD4HrPJ6tJibEjbsF7CdRhqkQkaSKhRIYYYLATmGwqz5A/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	真心不巧，它确确实实就是在一个超现代化的城市边上。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【雅典卫城】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	希腊雅典卫城修建于公元前5世纪，集古希腊建筑与雕刻艺术之大成。雅典卫城是希腊最杰出的古建筑群，日漫《圣斗士星矢》十二星座设定也是源自于这里哦~\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWLKKSUNlVGepSibc2hF6ulgwFZZkBicWQ6OCrzseqzhwaZWaqHWAT9mhg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	宏伟而壮观，当然，实际上……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWQib2PAId194WRqr8Tmwp26nrFNb9TMS291Dvh3hD65C5TLIicg33OBdw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	被城市包围就只剩下一座山了……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【拉什莫尔山】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	拉什莫尔山，或译为若虚莫山，俗称美国总统公园、美国总统山、总统雕像山，雕刻着美国历史上著名的前总统头像，他们分别是华盛顿、杰斐逊、老罗斯福和林肯。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWgAiccNAWXX4liaM8AiaBmicyn0YAM6jTtEydic1bBUPia3ZmKPEMOIYhyc5A/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	看上去是很壮观的对吧，但是真相是……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWjclF4l4Zw2KyLbyTQywpKDRH2KiaVdo5m0oViafzCe57ickO8Y0S0S08w/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	就在山上雕了那么一点？？\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【蒙娜丽莎的微笑】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	蒙娜丽莎是意大利文艺复兴时代著名画家达·芬奇的肖像画作品。法国·巴黎卢浮宫博物馆的镇馆三宝之一。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoW48DxsLgHLZCmp83ILFQpicB6m2ZpIazficS8Neq8U9zdEmErmjmibBicVQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	BUT……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWiaGSQjCm2LDBUVF5Eyiazx6lHINiaFiaP30cJickTnlVZUYibCzj3gQz6Haw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	⋯⋯请告诉我，蒙娜丽莎君你在哪？卢浮宫不带这么玩儿的吧！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【小美人鱼】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	小美人鱼铜像是一座世界闻名的铜像，她位于丹麦哥本哈根市中心东北部的长堤公园(Langelinie)。远望这个人身鱼尾的美人鱼，她坐在一块巨大的花岗石上，恬静娴雅，悠闲自得；走近这座铜像，您看到的却是一个神情忧郁、冥思苦想的少女。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWmib881x7LglUiccHOzjoYcJz1cCNKjFkXibB79mt2Y9NTFUibgG4EeYZHQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	美丽的小美人鱼，每天来游客一定多到爆吧，然而……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWmXo0RL0wrXDmWMCzPEsPY64AjoNsnSMaDRqtGWESl3ickTibec3QicSoQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	哦呵呵呵呵呵⋯⋯还真是小小小小美人鱼⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【美国曼哈顿中央公园】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	中央公园英文为Central \r\nPark，是全世界大都市中最美的城市公园，被誉为纽约之肺。340公顷的宏大面积使她与自由女神、帝国大厦等同为纽约乃至美国的象征。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWaHsbgEVbjUlRNNOEK2JaGSebib9afcaS9qU3Rdwo3ohVSnsMbUbvYfg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWOfY92vAaTDQ66GPh32EAGoPAF1XISqvfvjZ94II7hK4nDw4L0G0O4Q/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	至于为什么叫做中央公园呢，实际上它……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/jm7nicU7AljqMKLzPFkLyC2Khl4wEPvoWoAeGhiavuxx9NjDxeLJY1pgExLTFiaCHCiavMZhGFLHx7b9S62kiaES9HA/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	真的特喵的在中央⋯⋯\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;【中国长城】&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Pfg6A2nYy4X1BVBiac1R3ibO8WrGdgqVMmXwmBLBjVE3wgFeT1r72MzgJKAcrTP12o7SicQqc46K0mfsdr8EIOiaBg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	你心中的长城是蜿蜒千万里，而事实上国庆期间你看到的是……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Pfg6A2nYy4X1BVBiac1R3ibO8WrGdgqVMmUqF81gzIMTFjylH0NnPP3Pgmfnk