ial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;联系电话：0871-68681294&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这年头安宁&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;女人无所谓正派&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;正派是因为引诱不够&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;男人无所谓忠诚&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;忠诚是因为背叛的筹码太低！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这年头安宁&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;你敢寻花问柳&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;我就敢红杏出墙&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;我宁愿你抱着别的女人想我&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;也不愿你抱着我想别的女人！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这年头安宁&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;女人谨记&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;一定要吃好穿好玩好睡好&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;一旦累死了&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;就有别的女人来，花咱的钱，&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;住咱的房，睡咱的老公，&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;泡咱的男朋友，还打咱的娃！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这年头安宁&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;到处是错别字&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;植树造零，勤捞致富，选霸干部，&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;为民储害，提钱释放，攻官小姐！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这年头安宁&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;苦干实干，做给天看；&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;东混西混，一凡风顺；&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;任劳任怨，永难如愿！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, 